Yet another video, which appears to show the administration of corporal punishment on a school premises, has emerged.ADVERTISINGinRead invented by Teads
The video, which spans fewer than 20 seconds, starts with a female teacher laying into a teenage girl with a stick or pipe, as the rest of the class screams and shouts.
The girl, who is backed against a wall, then begins pushing the teacher.
The teacher falls backwards, onto a desk and the girl then runs off.
